                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12671235" author="shubhamc" created="Fri, 6 Feb 2009 18:38:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This happens because the optimizer eliminates the limit after a sort and puts an attribute in POSort/LOSort instead. This attribute is not used in the local mode sorting as this would adversely affect the MR sorting of the samples.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have modified the code to avoid that optimization happening when executing in the local mode. I have also added a couple of test cases that verify the plans in both local and MR mode.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12671328" author="olgan" created="Fri, 6 Feb 2009 21:26:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am reviewing this patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12671360" author="olgan" created="Fri, 6 Feb 2009 22:35:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch committed, thanks, Shubham!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
